text: hi my name is pumpernickel  i have a hammer and a sickle i like to fix tricycles, bicycles,  even some vehicles, but one day a lady came with a dill pickle.   i did not know what to do so i fixed it to a popsicle so when i gave it back she was happy.  so now i know how to fix bicycles, tricycles, vehicles and dill pickles

title: My Hat
author: nicole
text: i had my hat one sunny day oh that cat i said he must have taken it away maybe i can snatch it from him while hes taking his nap i snuck into the house and found sap on my hat

title: Boxes
author: nicole
text: boxes are fun boxes are tons and tons of fun  building forts and towers   give you power.         no matter the weather     rain or sun     playing with boxes. . .     are tons of fun.

title: My Doggy
author: nicole
text: as funny as goofy in disney world,  as hyper as a little kid with a sugar rush,  as fluffy as a marshmallow waiting to be eaten,  is my comfy, cozy and playful dog charlie

title: Awesomeness
author: nicole
text: i'm so awesome  i met an opossum the opossum was impossible  so i ditched the possum  and met a bull the bull grunted  so off i went to meet the snake the snake slivered to much for me so i ran off and met a bee i then bumped into three i was tired  and all of these animals started to attack me so i made friends with a tree
